data.description: Seller is offering $5K in Flex Money to the Buyer's lender which can be used to buy down the rate, pay closing costs or adjust the purchase price! It has also passed FHA appraisal! WELCOME TO YOUR WATERFRONT OASIS! This charming 3Bed/2Bath manufactured home invites you to savor tranquil mornings by the water's edge with your favorite brew. Feel the comfort of a newer AC and bask in the updated living and dining spaces adorned with fresh paint and take comfort in knowing the roof was replaced in 2016. Whether you're embarking on homeownership or expanding your investment portfolio, this property is your perfect match. With an enticing price and a view that's truly worth a million, this opportunity is too good to pass up! Call now for your private showing!
